... Minimal reproducer for jmp L1 / L1: placement bug.
... This is what the parser source does:
...   1. SkrivNyRad jmp L1  →  generates "jmp L1" in output assembly
...   2. SkrivNyRad L1:      →  generated when first non-FUNKTION/DECLARE token is seen
...
... Bug: L1: lands right after hantera's ret, inside GE handler,
...      so jmp L1 jumps to wrong code. main loop at end is unreachable.

Funktion hello med unused
    ge unused
Hejdå

SkrivNyRad .text
SkrivNyRad .globl main
SkrivNyRad main:
SkrivNyRad push %r12
SkrivNyRad push %r13
SkrivNyRad push %rbp
SkrivNyRad subq $32, %rsp
SkrivNyRad call SetConsoleOutputCP
SkrivNyRad jmp L1

... --- these should run after L1 but L1 is in wrong place ---
SkrivNyRad hello:
SkrivNyRad mov $42, %rax
SkrivNyRad ret
SkrivNyRad L1:
SkrivNyRad call hello
SkrivNyRad addq $32, %rsp
SkrivNyRad pop %rbp
SkrivNyRad pop %r13
SkrivNyRad pop %r12
SkrivNyRad ret
